_sText:
A look at crumbling Chernobyl


Background:
This map is based off the S.T.A.L.K.E.R Universe. I took in account the visual style of Chernobyl while developing the map. The map shows a desolate town in Chernobyl that has been taken over by nature.

Support:
Cubemaps, Camping Spots/Barricade areas, 64 Spawnpoints
